        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/marsalam/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Luxor</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Cunoscut ca si orasul palatelor - numeroasele monumente te vor duce catre tara faraonilor.
        Vei vizita complexul de temple Karnak, construit in timpul anilor 1500 si desigur parfumeria. Croaziera pe Nill conta cost ( 5$ pentru voluntar).
        Cei 2 colosi al lui Memnon de 18 metri. Viziteaza in templul Hatshepsut singura femeie faraon cunoscuta in istorie.
        Trecere pe langa casa arheologistului Howard Carter, care a descoperit mormantul lui Tutanchamon in 1922.
        Shopping in fabrica de alabasrtu, bilete contra cost pentru vizitarea cladirilor antice, autobuz de transfer cu aer conditionat, pranzul ( bauturile sunt conta cost )
        Plecarea se face devreme, ajungand pe la ora 23:00
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        marti
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Known for being called a „city of pallaces”- the numerous monuments willbring You to the Pharaohs country. 
        You will visit Karnak Temple – complex built during 1500y. and also perfumery. Cruise on Nile is extra 
        chargeable on the place by 5$ for volunteers. 18m high Memnon’s 2 Colossus. Visit in Temple Hatshepsut – the 
        only kown Woman Pharaoh in history. Tresspass near the house of Howard Carter-archeologist, who discovered 
        the tomb of Tutanchamon in 1922. Visit in famous King Valley, where You will visit 3 tombs of egyptian lords. 
        Shopping in alabaster manufactury. extra charge tickets for visiting ancient buildings, air-conditioned bus 
        transfer, lunch (drinks extra charge). Departure at early time, arrival at around 23:00 PM.
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Tuesday
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>